response.overview: A lifetime of taking shots has ended Rocky’s career, and a crooked accountant has left him broke. Inspired by the memory of his trainer, however, Rocky finds glory in training and takes on an up-and-coming boxer.
response.tagline: In Russia, he fought the greatest fight of his life. Now...where does a champion go when he takes off the gloves?
